    "<b>Cursed Arrows</b> are <linked>Hardmode</linked> <linked>arrows</linked> which apply the <linked>Cursed Inferno</linked> <linked>debuff</linked> on contact with an <linked>enemy</linked>. Unlike <linked>Flaming Arrows</linked>, they do not go out when they hit <linked>water</linked>. They are <linked>the Corruption</linked> counterpart to <linked>the Crimson</linked>'s <linked>Ichor Arrows</linked>.",
